:

*"Njen otac je bio dobar čovek" (Her father was a good man).

*"Otac mu je preminuo pre nekoliko godina" (His father passed away a few years ago).

*"Oni su svi sinovi mog oca" (They are all sons of my father).

*"Koliko puta je otac radio preko vikenda?" (How many times did father work on the weekends?).

*"On je rekao da će njegov otac biti tu" (He said his father would be there).

*"Očevi su najbolji prijatelji njihovih dece" (Fathers are the best friends of their children).